Main Readme 


Installation 
1. Install NodeJS:https://nodejs.org/en/

2. Install Docker desktop: https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop.

3. git clone this repository. 

4. change directory to /dublin_bus_app/app in terminal.

5. execute npm run build

6. change directory to /dublin_bus_app in terminal.

7. execute docker-compose up, then check http://localhost:8000/ 


Local developing enviroment setting

1. pip install requirement.txt to conda virtual environment: 
  - pip install -r ./requirement.txt
2. After develop on local machine if there are some new dependency, update the requirement.txt
  - pip freeze > requirement.txt
